# alternateIds

**Instance Property**

A list of alternate Place IDs that identify a feature.

## Declaration

```swift
alternateIds?: string[];
```

## Discussion

These values associate alternate identifiers with a place that changes its identity over time. For information about place identifiers, see [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/MapKit/identifying-unique-locations-with-place-ids].
